# Capacitor Android Build Workflow

When making changes to web assets (HTML, CSS, JS) that need to be tested on Android:

1. Run `npm run cap:sync:android` (cross-platform build; no rsync required on Windows)
2. Open Android Studio: `npx cap open android` or open the `android/` folder
3. **Build → Clean Project** if assets seem stale
4. Run on emulator or USB device

Verify toolchain: `.\scripts\check-android-toolchain.ps1`

Push setup: see [docs/android.md](../docs/android.md) and `.\scripts\check-android-push.ps1`

Always edit source files at the repo root, not under `www/`.
